## Known Schema Facts

- `int_game_team_features` has an `opponent` column — use it directly
- `conference` is NOT in `int_game_team_features` — join to `int_team_season_features`
- `is_home` is NOT in `int_game_team_features` — derive via join to `raw.games`
- `int_game_environment` uses `home_team` / `away_team` not `team_name`
- All numeric columns from psycopg2 return as Decimal — cast to float64 immediately
- Boolean columns: `.map(lambda x: 1 if x is True else (0 if x is False else np.nan)).astype(float)`
- `int_game_team_features` granularity: two rows per game (one per team)
- `sp_rating` and `conference`: authoritative source is `int_team_season_features`
- EPA in `raw.plays` is named `ppa`
- Score differential in `raw.plays`: `offense_score - defense_score` (from offense perspective)
- Quarter in `raw.plays` is named `period`
- `int_game_model_features`: condemned — do not use, do not reference
- Pac-12: G5 for all seasons (post-realignment)
- Notre Dame: P4 — route by team name not conference label
- UConn: G5 — route by team name not conference label

